{"tid":222831,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"內地警察局資深所長的建議，八個{一律}保護您～","createTime":"2017-04-29T21:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T17:00:58.000Z","uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5eeac5371c86c680505c49972041e7821b41e6d9","tid":222831,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T21:38:56.000Z","msg":"內地警察局資深所長的建議<br />\n八個{一律}保護您～<br />\n<br />\n(1)接電話，不管是誰，只要談到銀行金融卡，一律掛掉。<br />\n(2)只要談到你中獎了，一律掛掉。<br />\n(3)只要聽到~公務、檢察官、法務部、稅務司、，一律掛掉。<br />\n4）所有短信，要點選「連結」的，一律刪掉。<br />\n5）陌生人發訊要「連結」的，一律不點。<br />\n6）所有170開頭的電話，一律不接。<br />\n7 ) line文說：妳轉傳幾人，會有好運的，一律刪除。<br />\n８) 所有測試算命的網站,尤其要先連結朋友才看到,一律不上<br />\n<br />\n能做到這個八個一律，<br />\n基本上就不會上當受騙了。"},{"pid":"69ab9f5a339320982a36f9a87ae2f456f90075dc","tid":222831,"uid":27866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T22:05:37.000Z","msg":"謝分享"},{"pid":"aa77c1946ea95696dac75741246fcf1dfefea776","tid":222831,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T22:09:36.000Z","msg":"感謝大大無私分享"},{"pid":"bc0c65fdf07deb039e5ef99c72334c751b381a67","tid":222831,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T23:55:22.000Z","msg":"Line?"},{"pid":"d05681d03225ba64232d097b4cd5289e6ad84dc0","tid":222831,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T00:18:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>感謝大大無私分享</blockquote><br />\n不用謝牙"},{"pid":"7ae4e93b267095eb01df431f41463552a6823cdb","tid":222831,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T01:39:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc518b15aee50e6b027ed6db612713540c1a6242","tid":222831,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T01:40:48.000Z","msg":"樓豬接到球，一律擋掉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b0be01c2c56f89f9ea1c6c1284ee8fac275a1b","tid":222831,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T02:45: